reviewText:
This video is not what you think it is. Oh, yeah, it does have a lot of real fights in it but not any good ones like you're wanting to see. If you wanna see some good fights and stuff then watch Jerry Springer - Bad Boys & Naughty Girls or Jerry Springer - Too Hot For TV!  But don't get this video. It's a real clunker! Avoid it!
P.S. Watch Ultimate Fighting instead of this!!![...]
